  <entry>
    <title>「慢慢好了，意识到人生偶然的节点」</title>
    <link href="https://ashburshui.github.io/2025/03/06/humble/%E6%85%A2%E6%85%A2%E5%A5%BD%E4%BA%86_%E6%84%8F%E8%AF%86%E5%88%B0%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E5%81%B6%E7%84%B6%E7%9A%84%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9/"/>
    <id>https://ashburshui.github.io/2025/03/06/humble/%E6%85%A2%E6%85%A2%E5%A5%BD%E4%BA%86_%E6%84%8F%E8%AF%86%E5%88%B0%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E5%81%B6%E7%84%B6%E7%9A%84%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9/</id>
    <published>2025-03-06T16:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2025-03-14T20:58:57.840Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>1)参与生活，对人和事深有兴趣 2)大大方方，好好说话 3)不揉合past emo不污染生活，不焦虑什么不懂就提高认知<br><span id="more"></span></p></blockquote><p><img src="/blog-images/earthrise.jpg" alt=""></p><p>和另一个<a href="https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%9A%97%E6%B7%A1%E8%97%8D%E9%BB%9E">link</a></p><p><u>Brand new to the world… —&gt;&gt; 1997 —&gt;&gt; 2002 —&gt;&gt; 2005 —&gt;&gt; 2008 —&gt;&gt; 2009 —&gt;&gt; 2013 —&gt;&gt; 2016 —&gt;&gt; 2018 —&gt;&gt; 2022 —&gt;&gt; 2025… —&gt;&gt; unknown</u>，懵懵懂懂，朦胧的直觉，每个节点好好学。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Milestone -1:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">有时候世界踹你一脚，未必是坏事，是危是机，看你怎么想🤔？</span><br><span class="line">实事求是，享受恐惧和成长的邀请，不断体会超越怨恨的好处</span><br><span class="line">暂时迷茫是可以接受的，不要一直off track，做正确的事情，靠谱的人</span><br><span class="line">...猴子，果汁，多巴胺(快乐一点都不长久)，想明白了沒？柔性，灰度的视角，😂停下来...慢慢来，love the messy stuff</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Milestone 0:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">错误的观念，把人憋得难受，而不是具体的事物，这也是relationship cost，谨慎地选择</span><br><span class="line">Show up, say Hi, get the work done，and... be mindful，学会厚脸皮navigate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Milestone 1:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">* 想明白啥是胡说八道，和高明的💉</span><br><span class="line">+ 定位到问题了，就认真处理1)对压力的反应 &amp; 2)深入的交往，do you really know them？悬崖边上，赶紧拉回来。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1)参与生活，对人和事深有兴趣 2)大大方方，好好说话 3)不揉合past emo不污染生活，不焦虑什么不懂就提高认知&lt;br&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
    
